### PPPoE Pages

#### [NEW] [pages/pppoe/PPPoEPage.tsx](file:///home/butterfly-student/programing/Mikrotik/gomikhmon/frontend/src/pages/pppoe/PPPoEPage.tsx)
A single tab-container page with 4 tabs:
1. **Secrets** ‚Äî CRUD table (name, profile, service, disabled toggle, edit/delete)
2. **Profiles** ‚Äî CRUD table (name, rate limit, local/remote address, session timeout)
3. **Active** ‚Äî Real-time via `usePPPActiveWS` (name, IP, uptime, traffic, kick button)
4. **Inactive** ‚Äî Real-time via `usePPPInactiveWS` (name, profile, last logged out)

Design follows same pattern as [HotspotPage.tsx](file:///home/butterfly-student/programing/Mikrotik/gomikhmon/frontend/src/pages/hotspot/HotspotPage.tsx): unified card, tab bar as header, sub-components per tab, modals for create/edit.

#### [NEW] [pages/pppoe/index.ts](file:///home/butterfly-student/programing/Mikrotik/gomikhmon/frontend/src/pages/pppoe/index.ts)
- Export `PPPoEPage`

---

